&lt;p&gt;We’re seeking a highly collaborative Business Intelligence Analyst / Engineer to serve as the critical link between our Treasury Finance team and technical data teams. This is a unique hybrid role for someone who thrives at the intersection of finance, data, and strategy—translating complex business needs into powerful data-driven solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you’ll work directly with Treasury stakeholders to support reporting, cash positioning, liquidity management, and funding strategies. You’ll leverage data from Microsoft SQL Server and Snowflake environments to deliver impactful analytics, dashboards, and data assets that drive financial insights, securitization modeling, performance tracking, and regulatory reporting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: Hooksett, NH (Hybrid)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
