&lt;li&gt;Partner with data engineering teams to identify data sources and deliver scalable solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain dashboards, reports, and analytical datasets supporting Treasury decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop robust data models, curated datasets, and semantic layers aligned with leasing business logic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform data profiling, validation, and reconciliation to ensure accuracy and consistency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support audit and compliance needs through documentation, data lineage, and reconciliation evidence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage multiple priorities and maintain clear communication with stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
