&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Fleet Performance. Maximize Asset Value. Lead Operational Excellence.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Merchants Fleet is seeking a strategic and results-driven Manager, Off Rent Program to lead the execution and optimization of our off-rent fleet operations. This high-impact leadership role is responsible for maximizing asset value from vehicle return through reconditioning and disposition, while driving operational efficiency, reducing cycle times, and improving overall fleet performance.&lt;/p&gt;
